    private class Tensor.TensorIterator
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.Iterator<T>
    Iterator of the entire tensor. Used to iterate over the entire tensor. The same as iterating using get method with one-dimensional index varying form 0 to width^dimCount-1.
